    "http://ogp.me/ns#title": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Empowering Women in the Music Industry | Artist showcase - Day 1 |  Thu, Apr 30, 2026, 7:00 pm | Fourth Stage"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#image": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "https://naccnaca-eventimages.s3.amazonaws.com/40721/ammoye_headshot_(damian_singh)_-_ammoye_music__large.jpeg"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "This event is part of the Empowering Women in the Music Industry Conference presented by Axé WorldFest in partnership with the National Arts Centre.\n\nShowcase schedule:\n\nDoors open – 6:30 PM\n\nMiss McLeod – 7:00 PM\n\nDIVKA – 7:35 PM\n\nTara Moneka – 8:25 PM\n\nAmmoye – 9:20 PM\n\nAbout the conference:\n\nEWIMI6 is a three-day, multi-venue conference and showcase program featuring 17 events across 9 venues, including live and DJ showcases, networking, pitching, keynotes, panels, workshops, mentorship, and wellness activities. \n\nThe 2026 theme, Cultural Connectors, highlights artists and cultural workers as bridges between communities and cultures, emphasizing..."
      }
    ],
