        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Miina | with Dana Sipos |  Fri, Apr 10, 2026, 8:00 pm | Fourth Stage"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#image": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "https://naccnaca-eventimages.s3.amazonaws.com/40312/web_size_miina_credit_erica_chan_web__large.jpg"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "In August 2023, Miina released her debut EP Slow Motion, an impeccable, multi-layered collection produced by Gus Van Go (Beaches, Metric). The release marked the start of a dynamic first year, during which Miina's singles Hiccup (featuring and co-written with acclaimed songwriter Lowell) and Pressure received extensive radio play across Canada. \n\nWriting for Rifflandia Magazine, Michael Luis captured the essence of her sound: “Miina is the sound of the sunlight cutting through the foliage. Everything is brighter, funkier, more danceable, but with love for the environment and human emotion.” \n\nHaving opened for celebrated artists..."
      }
    ],
